OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778245867
OL,3,CWhat went wrong for Labour in the
OL,4,CNorth West?
OL,6,FThe Labour Party suffered huge losses
OL,7,Facross the North West in a local
OL,8,Felection that many saw as a referendum
OL,9,Fon Prime Minister Keir Starmer's
OL,10,Fleadership.
OL,12,FLabour's dismal performance in
OL,13,FThursday's polls culminated in the
OL,14,Floss of Tameside Council, a stronghold
OL,15,Fsince 1979.
OL,17,FIn the early hours of Friday, Tameside
OL,18,FCouncil Leader Eleanor Wills described
OL,19,Fit as a night of 'deep sadness'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/18
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
