PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778245867
OL,3,CWhat went wrong for Labour in the
OL,4,CNorth West?
OL,6,FBut on Friday morning, the Prime
OL,7,FMinister claimed he will stand as
OL,8,FPrime Minister at the next election -
OL,9,Fand refused to resign.
OL,11,FThe results in Tameside deprives
OL,12,FLabour of power after an uninterrupted
OL,13,Frun of 47 years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/18
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
