PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778245867
OL,3,CWhat went wrong for Labour in the
OL,4,CNorth West?
OL,6,FThe party lost 14 of the 15 seats it
OL,7,Fwas defending ` enough to deprive it
OL,8,Fof a majority and leave the council
OL,9,Fwith no group large enough to have
OL,10,Foverall control. The new state of the
OL,11,Fparties is Labour 25 seats, Reform 19,
OL,12,Findependents eight and the
OL,13,FConservatives five.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/18
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778245867
OL,3,CWhat went wrong for Labour in the
OL,4,CNorth West?
OL,6,FLabour Councillor Eleanor Wills spoke
OL,7,Fto ITV Granada shortly after the
OL,8,Fresults were declared. She said:
OL,9,F"We've lost some community minded
OL,10,Fpeople that have dedicated lots of
OL,11,Fyears to the heart of their community,
OL,12,Freal value, understanding Tameside and
OL,13,Fthe people they represent.
OL,15,FShe praised local candidates for their
OL,16,Fwork in what she described as a 'toxic
OL,17,Fcampaign', but stopped short of
OL,18,Fcalling for change at the top of the
OL,19,Fparty.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/18
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778245867
OL,3,CWhat went wrong for Labour in the
OL,4,CNorth West?
OL,6,F"I do think it's evident that this is
OL,7,Fa national vote. At many doors that
OL,8,Fwe've tried to knock on, there's
OL,9,Falways been some misunderstanding
OL,10,Fbetween national politics and local
OL,11,Fpolitics."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/18
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778245867
OL,3,CWhat went wrong for Labour in the
OL,4,CNorth West?
OL,6,F"I think it's time for us to go back
OL,7,Fand reflect and look at what we're
OL,8,Fdoing as a party, we need to
OL,9,Fcollectively go back and reflect. I
OL,10,Fthink the fear is seeing the council
OL,11,Fin no overall control means we're now
OL,12,Fgoing to delay progress and that's a
OL,13,Freal frustration. Actually this
OL,14,Fgovernment for the first time has
OL,15,Fstarted to invest in authorities,
OL,16,Fwe've had more money through this
OL,17,Fgovernment which has meant we've been
OL,18,Fable to do more. "
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/18
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
