PN,39112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778245867
OL,3,CWhat went wrong for Labour in the
OL,4,CNorth West?
OL,6,FLabour council leader Alistair Bradley
OL,7,Fsaid he welcomed challenge, but that
OL,8,Fit had to come with a purpose.
OL,10,FReflecting on the reasons for a
OL,11,Fbruising night for Labour in the
OL,12,Fborough, Labour council leader
OL,13,FAlistair Bradley pointed towards
OL,14,Fcentral government ` although he did
OL,15,Fnot identify a deficiency in policy,
OL,16,Fbut rather presentation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/18
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778245867
OL,3,CWhat went wrong for Labour in the
OL,4,CNorth West?
OL,6,F"Labour's doing some great stuff `
OL,7,Fwaiting lists are coming down, (there
OL,8,Fare) better standards in schools,
OL,9,F(improved) renters' rights ` but it's
OL,10,Fbeen buried by a lot of nonsense about
OL,11,Fleaderships and distractions around
OL,12,Fthe Westminster bubble," the veteran
OL,13,Fpolitician said.
OL,15,FSpeaking on Friday morning, Prime
OL,16,FMinister said he's not going to walk
OL,17,Faway, despite Labour losses across the
OL,18,FUK.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@`pmpD@DpnqD@ApmqD@JpntD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/18
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
