PN,39114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778245867
OL,3,CWhat went wrong for Labour in the
OL,4,CNorth West?
OL,6,FHe said: "The results are tough, they
OL,7,Fare very tough, and there's no
OL,8,Fsugarcoating it.
OL,10,F"We have lost brilliant Labour
OL,11,Frepresentatives across the country,
OL,12,Fthese are people who put so much into
OL,13,Ftheir communities, so much into our
OL,14,Fparty.
OL,16,F"And that hurts, and it should hurt,
OL,17,Fand I take responsibility."
OL,26,@nD@JOUrD@AOUxD@AOUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/18
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
