OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778245867
OL,3,CWhat went wrong for Labour in the
OL,4,CNorth West?
OL,6,FHe'd earlier told Labour members:
OL,7,F"We've made some big calls, to
OL,8,Fstabilise our public finances, to
OL,9,Finvest in our public services, not to
OL,10,Fget dragged into a war in Iran.
OL,12,F"But we've also made unnecessary
OL,13,Fmistakes, one of which was that
OL,14,Falthough we were right to level with
OL,15,Fthe public about the scale and depth
OL,16,Fof the challenges we face, we didn't
OL,17,Fdo enough to convince them that things
OL,18,Fwill get better, that things will
OL,19,Fimprove, the hope.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/18
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39116
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778245867
OL,3,CWhat went wrong for Labour in the
OL,4,CNorth West?
OL,6,F"And that is why in the coming days
OL,7,FI'm going to set out the steps that we
OL,8,Fwill take to deliver the change that
OL,9,Fthey want and that they deserve."
OL,11,FHe added: "These are tough results but
OL,12,Ftough days like this, they don't
OL,13,Fweaken my resolve to deliver the
OL,14,Fchange that I promised at the general
OL,15,Felection, they strengthen my resolve
OL,16,Fto do so."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@aO]sD@KOUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/18
